.\" kilonode/docs/man/kilonoded.8
.Dd May 26, 2026
.Dt KILONODED 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm kilonoded
.Nd KiloNode local packet node and BBS daemon
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Fl -config Ar path
.Op Fl -check-config
.Op Fl -foreground
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
reads a KiloNode-native config file, opens enabled local KISS transports, feeds
KISS frames into the AX.25 monitor path, and exposes local control and shell
interfaces when configured.
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl -config Ar path
Read the daemon config from
.Ar path .
.It Fl -check-config
Parse and validate the config, then exit.
.It Fl -foreground
Run in the foreground. Background daemon mode is not implemented yet.
.It Fl -help
Show command usage.
.El
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Pa /etc/kilonode/kilonode.conf
Suggested Linux and OpenBSD config path.
.It Pa /usr/local/etc/kilonode/kilonode.conf
Suggested FreeBSD and NetBSD config path.
.El
.Sh EXAMPLES
.Dl kilonoded --config /etc/kilonode/kilonode.conf --foreground
.Dl kilonoded --config packaging/examples/kilonode-minimal.conf --check-config
.Sh SECURITY NOTES
Run with the least privileges practical. Keep shell listeners bound to localhost
unless a later authenticated public access mode is added.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr kilonodectl 1 ,
.Xr kilonode-monitor 1
.Sh AUTHORS
KiloNode is developed by M6VPN.
